---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Attività sulla Costa Azzurra — Mas du Chanoine" description="Scoprite le attività e le visite da fare dal Mas du Chanoine sulla Costa Azzurra." lang="it">
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-28 px-4 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-100"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 text-accent-600 font-light">Da scoprire</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary-900">Attività sulla Costa Azzurra</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-content">
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">La posizione centrale del nostro B&B vi permetterà di andare in giro su tutta la Costa Azzurra in base ai vostri desideri.</p>
        <h2>Visite consigliate sulla Costa Azzurra</h2>
        <p>Nella regione ci sono parecchi luoghi turistici da non perdere durante il vostro soggiorno. Potrete scoprire molti villaggi fortificati, visitare Nizza, raggiungere il Principato di Monaco, fare una passeggiata sulla Croisette a Cannes.</p>
        <h2>Sport</h2>
        <p>È possibile raggiungere le spiagge di Cagnes-sur-Mer a meno di 5 km dalla casa. Per gli appassionati di golf, ci sono 10 percorsi di golf accessibili in un raggio di 15 km.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
        <a href="/it/activites/saint-paul-de-vence/" class="group relative block rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <div class="aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden"><img src="/media/activites/saint-paul.jpg" alt="Saint-Paul de Vence" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/80 via-primary-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-5 text-white"><h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold">Saint-Paul de Vence</h2></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/it/activites/nizza/" class="group relative block rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <div class="aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden"><img src="/media/activites/nice.jpg" alt="Nizza" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/80 via-primary-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-5 text-white"><h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold">Nizza</h2></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/it/activites/monaco-2/" class="group relative block rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <div class="aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden"><img src="/media/activites/monaco.jpg" alt="Monaco" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/80 via-primary-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-5 text-white"><h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold">Monaco</h2></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/it/activites/cannes-e-isole-lerins/" class="group relative block rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <div class="aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden"><img src="/media/activites/cannes.jpg" alt="Cannes" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/80 via-primary-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-5 text-white"><h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold">Cannes e Isole Lérins</h2></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/it/activites/antibes-e-cap-dantibes/" class="group relative block rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <div class="aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden"><img src="/media/activites/antibes.jpg" alt="Antibes" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/80 via-primary-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-5 text-white"><h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold">Antibes e Cap d'Antibes</h2></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/it/activites/i-villaggi-collinari/" class="group relative block rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
          <div class="aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden"><img src="/media/activites/villages.jpg" alt="Villaggi collinari" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/80 via-primary-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-5 text-white"><h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold">I villaggi collinari</h2></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-4">Esplorate la Costa Azzurra dal Mas</h2>
      <a href="https://masduchanoine.thais-hotel.com/hotel/website/reservations.php?lang=it" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary bg-white text-primary-900 hover:bg-primary-100">Prenota ora</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
